01:12:47,071 --> 01:12:49,315
[GIGGLES]
That's what you think.

986
01:12:49,323 --> 01:12:51,487
That was the longest
three weeks of my life.

987
01:12:51,492 --> 01:12:53,326
<i>[BEEPING]</i>

988
01:12:57,290 --> 01:12:58,703
