<i>[MUFFLED MAN'S VOICE]</i>

1067
01:17:27,059 --> 01:17:29,849
<i>[COUNTRY MUSIC PLAYING]</i>

1068
01:17:39,613 --> 01:17:40,901
<i>[SETS PARKING BRAKE]</i>

