1103
01:21:38,143 --> 01:21:40,307
[SCREAMING]

1104
01:21:54,576 --> 01:21:55,864
Let's go.

1105
01:22:03,419 --> 01:22:05,538
Everything's under control.

1106
01:22:05,546 --> 01:22:06,709
Good.

1107
01:22:11,468 --> 01:22:13,632
<i>[FOOTSTEPS]</i>

1108
01:22:20,936 --> 01:22:23,771
[FEMALE HUMMING "RIDE OF THE VALKYRIES"]

1109
01:22:34,116 --> 01:22:35,154
[CLUNK]

