1121
01:23:04,771 --> 01:23:05,729
[CLUNK]

1122
01:23:07,399 --> 01:23:09,859
<i>[ALARM SOUNDING]</i>

1123
01:23:22,664 --> 01:23:24,657
Life support systems.

1124
01:23:26,335 --> 01:23:27,703
