1126
01:23:30,380 --> 01:23:32,715
<i>Now, Wilson!</i>

1127
01:23:32,716 --> 01:23:35,256
<i>Forget the door!
Turn off the alarm!</i>

1128
01:23:39,223 --> 01:23:40,306
Uh!

